description:
Kate and Doree discuss their non-skincare daily routines, and how great Q-tips feel. (Yeah, we know you're not supposed to stick them in your ears, but...) Then, they answer listener questions about what to do when you feel like your story has already been told, and how to stay vulnerable when you’re faced with rejection and heartbreak.

To learn more, visit forever35podcast.com.

Theme music by Riot.
